# endDate

**Instance Property**

The result’s end time and date.

## Declaration

```swift
var endDate: Date { get }
```

## Discussion

The result’s `endDate` is always one minute or less after the [doc://com.apple.coremotion/documentation/CoreMotion/CMTremorResult/startDate].

## Reading the Time Interval

- **startDate**: The result’s start time and date.
